high_descs: In bedroom head towards the door turn left to the sofa side.
Take the ladle from the sofa.
Turn left again turn left to Reach the bowl on the wooden table.
Place the ladle on a bowl in the wooden table.
Take the bowl along with the spoon.
Turn left head towards the diningtable.
Place the bowl on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Take the ladle and bowl and place them on the dining table.

high_descs: Turn a round, walk out through a left exit, continue along the left side of a sofa and face the sofa approximately in the middle.
Pick up the ladle from the sofa.
Turn around to see a bowl in front of you, walk around it to the its opposite side and face it.
Place the ladle inside a bowl on the table.
Pick up the bowl from the table.
Turn left where you see a white diningtable, walk to this diningtable, then walk further to its long side and turn towards it.
Place the bowl on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Place the ladle with the spoon inside on the white diningtable.

high_descs: Stand up turn around move towards the sofa.
Take the ladle from the sofa.
Turn around move towards the bowl.
Keep the ladle inside the bowl.
Take the bowl from the table.
Turn around move towards the dining table.
Keep the bowl on the dining table.
anns.task_desc: Take the ladle, keep it inside the bowl and keep the bowl on the dining table.
